spec_data.Name: python-repoze-lru
spec_data.Description:
repoze.lru is a LRU (least recently used) cache implementation. Keys and values
that are not used frequently will be evicted from the cache faster than keys
and values that are used frequently.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 03:32:07 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A tiny LRU cache implementation and decorator
